dcterms:creator: Tensorflow
dcterms:description: A dataset generated by capturing aerial footage of the target from an altitude of 20-30 meters, consisting of 5 videos at 30 frames per second and 1100 keyframes annotated with a bounding box enclosing the target. The dataset includes images with targets at different angles, varied lighting and background conditions, and pictures deliberately without a target.
dcterms:title: Aerial footage dataset for target detection
